## Style guide

- SEC 8-K register: extremely brief and factual. Typically 1-3 pages.
- Item 2.02 earnings 8-Ks: the 8-K itself is ~1 page of boilerplate; the real content is in the Exhibit 99.1 press release.
- No promotional language. Legal boilerplate only.
- Safe-harbor statement for forward-looking statements.
- For Item 2.02: explicitly state "The information in this Item 2.02, including Exhibit 99.1 attached hereto, is being furnished and shall not be deemed 'filed' for purposes of Section 18 of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934."

## Output format

Return the filing as clean markdown. Start with the cover page. No JSON wrapping.
